WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.667
SwingVantage saves your data on your device and syncs it to your account, so your progress is safe across devices.

2
00:00:05.667 --> 00:00:11.333
Tap Download Backup to save a complete copy: sessions, profiles, equipment, progress, and badges.

3
00:00:11.333 --> 00:00:17.000
You can password-protect the file.

4
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.667
Keep that password safe — without it, an encrypted backup cannot be recovered.

5
00:00:22.667 --> 00:00:28.333
To restore, upload the file and preview what comes back.

6
00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:34.000
Use Merge to add without deleting, or Replace for a full reset.
